item.title: Help!
item.dc:creator: @0_Deni_0 0 Deni 0
item.description:
@0_Deni_0 wrote:

rightclick with ur mouse at compiler… then click edit…
you should see a text…
remove the text and add this :

@echo off
title Compiler
“C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_04\bin\javac.exe” -cp . *.java
pause

(then save)
